123
00:06:11,525 --> 00:06:12,200
Hello.

124
00:06:13,290 --> 00:06:14,750
Are you Miss Gu’s father?

125
00:06:14,790 --> 00:06:15,300
I am.

126
00:06:16,375 --> 00:06:17,208
Who are you?

127
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:18,775
I’m a journalist.

128
00:06:19,165 --> 00:06:21,458
