188
00:08:25,650 --> 00:08:26,275
OK.

189
00:08:26,375 --> 00:08:27,675
What do you want? I’ll go shopping.

190
00:08:27,790 --> 00:08:28,425
What do you want?

191
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:31,290
