280
00:13:16,625 --> 00:13:17,875
Just finished after-school classes.

281
00:13:18,825 --> 00:13:19,425
I see.

282
00:13:21,475 --> 00:13:22,125
Well.

283
00:13:23,375 --> 00:13:24,666
If there’s anything that upsets you,

284
00:13:24,875 --> 00:13:25,666
